    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10981: [FuseRead FuseBurn] File Based Miniflow.'
'Merged PR 10442: [CherryPick] [57271] [PR 10301] [FuseBurn] Enable default fuseburn ituff when ExitPort not 1 (FailPort).'
'Merged PR 10282: Merged PR 10276: [PrimeFuseBurnMaskTestMethod] Fuseburn without patmod/override'
'Merged PR 10046: [CherryPick] Merged PR 9867: [FuseBurn] Enable ULTEncode as MiniFlow API.'
'Merged PR 9773: Merged PR 9729: Fixing broken links and wiki generation process'
'Merged PR 9754: [CherryPick] Merged PR 9682: [FuseBurn][Mask][Sspec] Store FinalFuseStringToBurn to user defined sharedstorage.'
'Merged PR 9636: [CherryPick] Merged PR 9635: Remove ENG header for FuseBurn code at Verify.'</releaseNotes>
